com.camerontec.catalys.util.marketdata

Interface IFixMarketDataInstrument

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<IInstrument>, IInstrument
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FixMarketDataInstrument

    public interface IFixMarketDataInstrument
extends IInstrument
    Interface for instruments that are stored in the Market Data Server when it is in Daisy Chain mode (i.e. both client and feed sides of the server are FIX). Some extra information is stored in the instrument in this case.
